snippet: Rafael Cabrera-Bello birdied 9 of his first 11 holes and shot a nine-under-par 63 for a two-stroke lead after the first round of the Dubai Desert Classic.
abstract: Rafael Cabrera-Bello takes first-round lead at the Dubai Desert Classic; other golf items noted.
